snippet: LEAD: The California Air Resources Board adopted strict auto emission rules Friday to compel production of a new generation of ultra-clean cars and fuels, toughening the strictest air quality controls in the nation....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: The California Air Resources Board adopted strict auto emission rules Friday to compel production of a new generation of ultra-clean cars and fuels, toughening the strictest air quality controls in the nation.

headline.main: California Adopts New Car Emission Rules
